
Release Notes

v1.0 rc1

Widgetset compilation. Clients Vaadin jars needed for widgetset compilation (vaadin-client.jar, vaadin-client-compiler.jar) located in separated directory "../ROOT/WEB-INF/vaadin-clients-jars/".

Change version. Approach to fetching Vaadin releases changed.

Change version. Release list ordered by release date.

Change version. First release has 05.10.2012 release date. All preceded releases have different jar names or directory structure.

System file separator used in all paths.

Liferay Vaadin plugin works in Liferay with Vaadin 6.* version.

Liferay Vaadin plugin creates backups of all files and restores them if something wrong during update.






